### ShiftBook Log Management Actions
### Base URL: http://localhost:4004/shiftbook/ShiftBookService

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/shiftbook/ShiftBookService
@auth = Basic alice:

### Add ShiftBook Entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/addShiftBookEntry
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "werks": "1000",
  "shoporder": "SO123456",
  "stepid": "0010",
  "split": "001",
  "workcenter": "WC001",
  "user_id": "operator.name@example.com",
  "category": "CATEGORY_ID",
  "subject": "Machine Maintenance Required",
  "message": "Machine #3 is showing irregular vibrations. Scheduled maintenance recommended."
}

